# ðŸŒ¦ Live Weather Forecasting System

## Problem Statement
Predict hourly temperature using historical and live weather data to help in short-term weather planning.

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas, NumPy
- TensorFlow (LSTM)
- Scikit-learn
- Streamlit
- Render (Deployment)

## Approach
- Collected historical weather data
- Performed time-series preprocessing
- Trained LSTM with sliding window technique
- Scaled data using MinMaxScaler
- Deployed model with Streamlit for live predictions

## Model Details
- Architecture: LSTM
- Window size: 24 hours
- Evaluation metric: RMSE

## Results
- Stable short-term predictions
- Live inference with real-time data updates

## Live Demo
ðŸ”— https://predict-weather-5xyr.onrender.com

## Future Improvements
- Add humidity, pressure, wind features
- Multi-step forecasting
- Model uncertainty estimation
